Pad.~, ^Costa~, ^Ces.~, ^Wagn.~, ^Quattro Fior.~, ^Ant.~,
^Greg.~, ^Triss.~, ^Cam.~, ^Kanneg.~, ^Streckf.~, ^Filal.~,
^Bl.~, ^Gus.~, ^Witte~, ^v. Hoffing.~, ^Nott.~, ^Bartsch~, ^v.
